        <ontology:hasDescription>Competition with industrial products of similar use (sweets, cereals and other snaks). Also, the hectares dedicated to organic oats and other spring cereals have decreased since 2012 in Norway (Eurostat). Overall the type of challenge faced by this VC is Current. This VC is classified as Innovative.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


